profileText: a Representative from Florida; born in Santa Ana, Orange County, Calif., May 6, 1989; B.S., University of West Florida, Pensacola, Fla., 2018; United States Air Force, 2009-2014; Oregon Air National Guard, 2017-2018; non-profit executive; political commentator; unsuccessful candidate for election to the One Hundred Seventeenth Congress in 2020; elected as a Republican to the One Hundred Eighteenth Congress (January 3, 2023–present).
